Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper focuses on developing a conversational agent that can understand both language and images, which falls under the scope of natural language processing and language understanding. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper also involves using image data and leveraging state-of-the-art computer vision techniques to improve the performance of the conversational agent. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper involves developing an AI agent that can perform multiple tasks related to language and vision, which falls under the scope of AI research. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper involves designing an architecture that combines multiple modules and training the model on multiple tasks, which falls under the scope of machine learning research. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper involves working with multimodal data (language and images) and developing a system that can handle multiple modalities, which falls under the scope of multimedia research.
